label: AM319L: 9-in-1 IAQ Sensor (without display)
description: AM319L is a 9-in-1 ambient monitoring sensor including measurements of temperature, humidity, CO2 concentration, TVOC, pressure, light, motion, PM2.5 & PM10, and HCHO/O3. Unlike AM319, it does not have a display for visual output. It transmits data to a network server using LoRaWANÂ® technology for remote monitoring.
